spec_data.Name: rocoto
spec_data.Description:
Rocoto is a small collection of reusable Modules for Google Guice
to make easier the task of loading java.util.Properties by reading
configuration files.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 09:31:31 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Expanded properties file parsing for Google Guice
